CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 12, 1941, pg. 12 reads: "Courier Cameras Click As Colorful Eastern Open Unfolds On South Park's Beautiful Golf Course...7. The trophies...Harris and staff photographers."
TitMainTitle: Table with boxes of U. S. Tiger golf balls and golf trophies, including one inscribed "E. G. A. Amateur Championship 1941 winner, fourth flight," for Eastern Open at South Park golf course
